    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/45a5225bc33377dc088e525cf4fb412d.poster.avif?t=1739398850\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/45a5225bc33377dc088e525cf4fb412d.webm?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/45a5225bc33377dc088e525cf4fb412d.mp4?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你感觉，每眨一下眼睛，它就离你近了一些。<br>已经过去好几天了。<br>只要一直盯着那个红色冰箱，就会没事的。对吧？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/cec8faa25a3db8eacc3d78d1bb9c5ac4.poster.avif?t=1739398850\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/cec8faa25a3db8eacc3d78d1bb9c5ac4.webm?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/cec8faa25a3db8eacc3d78d1bb9c5ac4.mp4?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>红色冰箱里的六个故事</strong><br><br>这是一款由六个不同的第一人称恐怖故事组成的游戏。<br>每个章节都有一个特定的主题和玩法。<br><br>与冰箱怪物的凝视比赛。迷宫般永远走不出去的医院走廊和档案馆密室。大雪纷飞的高速公路上的灵异之旅……各种离奇故事，待您解锁。<br><br>在完整的游戏中体验更多阈限空间，与离奇古怪的陌生人来一场超现实的相遇。<br><br>这一切之间会不会有着某种联系？你能揭开红色冰箱里隐藏的巨大秘密吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/58733d20f794fc8438413c10759011cb.poster.avif?t=1739398850\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/58733d20f794fc8438413c10759011cb.webm?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/58733d20f794fc8438413c10759011cb.mp4?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>模拟恐怖</strong><br><br>在PSX时代的复古恐怖氛围中，踏上一场跌宕起伏、环环相扣的诡异旅行。<br><br>开启模拟后处理和锁帧，获享真正的沉浸式体验。<br>你有供你存档的记忆卡吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/3bc7e4c1c77d2fe188c45c6803621365.poster.avif?t=1739398850\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/3bc7e4c1c77d2fe188c45c6803621365.webm?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1532460/extras/3bc7e4c1c77d2fe188c45c6803621365.mp4?t=1739398850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
